Accessing Small SemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid AllSmallSemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid is an accessor function for accessing the complete list of non-isomorphic SemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid of orders 2 to 3.

Checking Models of Small SemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid
"IsASmallSemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid" is a function for checking a model against the complete list of non-isomorphic SemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid of orders 2 to 3. It returns true if the model is a Small SemicommutativeTernaryGroupoid, false otherwise.
